18#include "PDFModulusPoly.h"
19#include "PDFModulusGF.h"

21#include <algorithm>
22#include <stdexcept>

24namespace ZXing {
25namespace Pdf417 {
26
27ModulusPoly::ModulusPoly(const ModulusGF& field, const std::vector<int>& coefficients) :
28 _field(&field)
29{
30 size_t coefficientsLength = coefficients.size();
31 if (coefficientsLength > 1 && coefficients[0] == 0) {
32 // Leading term must be non-zero for anything except the constant polynomial "0"
33 size_t firstNonZero = 1;
34 while (firstNonZero < coefficientsLength && coefficients[firstNonZero] == 0) {
35 firstNonZero++;
36 }
37 if (firstNonZero == coefficientsLength) {
38 _coefficients.resize(1, 0);
39 }
40 else {
41 _coefficients.resize(coefficientsLength - firstNonZero);
42 std::copy(coefficients.begin() + firstNonZero, coefficients.end(), _coefficients.begin());
43 }
44 }
45 else {
46 _coefficients = coefficients;
47 }
48}
49
50/**
51* @return evaluation of this polynomial at a given point
52*/
53int
54ModulusPoly::evaluateAt(int a) const
55{
56 if (a == 0) {
57 // Just return the x^0 coefficient
58 return coefficient(0);
59 }
60 size_t size = _coefficients.size();
61 if (a == 1) {
62 // Just the sum of the coefficients
63 int result = 0;
64 for (int coefficient : _coefficients) {
65 result = _field->add(result, coefficient);
66 }
67 return result;
68 }
69 int result = _coefficients[0];
70 for (size_t i = 1; i < size; i++) {
71 result = _field->add(_field->multiply(a, result), _coefficients[i]);
72 }
73 return result;
74}
75
76ModulusPoly
77ModulusPoly::add(const ModulusPoly& other) const
78{
79 if (_field != other._field) {
80 throw std::invalid_argument("ModulusPolys do not have same ModulusGF field");
81 }
82 if (isZero()) {
83 return other;
84 }
85 if (other.isZero()) {
86 return *this;
87 }
88
89 auto smallerCoefficients = &_coefficients;
90 auto largerCoefficients = &other._coefficients;
91 if (smallerCoefficients->size() > largerCoefficients->size()) {
92 std::swap(smallerCoefficients, largerCoefficients);
93 }
94 std::vector<int> sumDiff(largerCoefficients->size());
95 size_t lengthDiff = largerCoefficients->size() - smallerCoefficients->size();
96
97 // Copy high-order terms only found in higher-degree polynomial's coefficients
98 std::copy_n(largerCoefficients->begin(), lengthDiff, sumDiff.begin());
99 for (size_t i = lengthDiff; i < largerCoefficients->size(); i++) {
100 sumDiff[i] = _field->add((*smallerCoefficients)[i - lengthDiff], (*largerCoefficients)[i]);
101 }
102 return ModulusPoly(*_field, sumDiff);
103}
104
105ModulusPoly
106ModulusPoly::subtract(const ModulusPoly& other) const
107{
108 if (_field != other._field) {
109 throw std::invalid_argument("ModulusPolys do not have same ModulusGF field");
110 }
111 if (other.isZero()) {
112 return *this;
113 }
114 return add(other.negative());
115}
116
117ModulusPoly
118ModulusPoly::multiply(const ModulusPoly& other) const
119{
120 if (_field != other._field) {
121 throw std::invalid_argument("ModulusPolys do not have same ModulusGF field");
122 }
123 if (isZero() || other.isZero()) {
124 return _field->zero();
125 }
126 auto& aCoefficients = _coefficients;
127 size_t aLength = aCoefficients.size();
128 auto& bCoefficients = other._coefficients;
129 size_t bLength = bCoefficients.size();
130 std::vector<int> product(aLength + bLength - 1, 0);
131 for (size_t i = 0; i < aLength; i++) {
132 int aCoeff = aCoefficients[i];
133 for (size_t j = 0; j < bLength; j++) {
134 product[i + j] = _field->add(product[i + j], _field->multiply(aCoeff, bCoefficients[j]));
135 }
136 }
137 return ModulusPoly(*_field, product);
138}
139
140ModulusPoly
141ModulusPoly::negative() const
142{
143 size_t size = _coefficients.size();
144 std::vector<int> negativeCoefficients(size);
145 for (size_t i = 0; i < size; i++) {
146 negativeCoefficients[i] = _field->subtract(0, _coefficients[i]);
147 }
148 return ModulusPoly(*_field, negativeCoefficients);
149}
150
151ModulusPoly
152ModulusPoly::multiply(int scalar) const
153{
154 if (scalar == 0) {
155 return _field->zero();
156 }
157 if (scalar == 1) {
158 return *this;
159 }
160 size_t size = _coefficients.size();
161 std::vector<int> product(size);
162 for (size_t i = 0; i < size; i++) {
163 product[i] = _field->multiply(_coefficients[i], scalar);
164 }
165 return ModulusPoly(*_field, product);
166}
167
168ModulusPoly
169ModulusPoly::multiplyByMonomial(int degree, int coefficient) const
170{
171 if (degree < 0) {
172 throw std::invalid_argument("degree < 0");
173 }
174 if (coefficient == 0) {
175 return _field->zero();
176 }
177 size_t size = _coefficients.size();
178 std::vector<int> product(size + degree, 0);
179 for (size_t i = 0; i < size; i++) {
180 product[i] = _field->multiply(_coefficients[i], coefficient);
181 }
182 return ModulusPoly(*_field, product);
183}
184
185void
186ModulusPoly::divide(const ModulusPoly& other, ModulusPoly& quotient, ModulusPoly& remainder) const
187{
188 if (_field != other._field) {
189 throw std::invalid_argument("ModulusPolys do not have same ModulusGF field");
190 }
191 if (other.isZero()) {
192 throw std::invalid_argument("Divide by 0");
193 }
194
195 quotient = _field->zero();
196 remainder = *this;
197
198 int denominatorLeadingTerm = other.coefficient(other.degree());
199 int inverseDenominatorLeadingTerm = _field->inverse(denominatorLeadingTerm);
200
201 while (remainder.degree() >= other.degree() && !remainder.isZero()) {
202 int degreeDifference = remainder.degree() - other.degree();
203 int scale = _field->multiply(remainder.coefficient(remainder.degree()), inverseDenominatorLeadingTerm);
204 ModulusPoly term = other.multiplyByMonomial(degreeDifference, scale);
205 ModulusPoly iterationQuotient = _field->buildMonomial(degreeDifference, scale);
206 quotient = quotient.add(iterationQuotient);
207 remainder = remainder.subtract(term);
208 }
209}
